You may want to create and edit the file:

	/accounts/devuser/pkg/etc/screenrc

to customize screen globally. Example configuration files have been
installed to:

	/accounts/devuser/pkg/share/examples/screen/screenrc
	/accounts/devuser/pkg/share/examples/screen/etcscreenrc

